{"tid":2023474,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[塔羅占卜] 入嚟放低煩惱同問題，有問必答（3）","createTime":"2020-05-19T04:44:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T07:44:46.000Z","uid":28251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"401d5d6430fdebfa037c46b7bea90b00cbaa172a","tid":2023474,"uid":28251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:44:29.000Z","msg":"幫你占卜，想比個方向你，幫你分擔啲煩惱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTG: <a href=\"http://t.me/xeolhcx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fxeolhcx&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F1EyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=58ea9756\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/xeolhcx</a><br />\n<strong>請直接係TG搵我，唔好留言，否則會miss咗，唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n留意！只限半年內嘅事件！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />建議事件性問題（如：我地嘅關係發展？佢對我有咩諗法？份工好唔好？）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />盡量避免時間性問題（如：幾時有拖拍？幾時可以復合？幾時有工開？）<br />\n<br />\n唔好問運程，因為唔係算命。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">1. 稱呼（中／英文名）<br />\n2. 如果問關係，對象稱呼（中／英文名）<br />\n3. 問題（越精簡越好）<br />\n4. 關係背景（作牌陣及解牌用，唔同關係會有唔同解釋）<br />\n註：LIHKG 搵到Post</span><br />\n<br />\n基於因果關係，如果任何人免費幫你占卜同你建立連繫，影響到你嘅決定，甚至左右到你嘅未來，佢都會有果報。為咗保障你我，恕我唔能夠免費占卜，我地之間有來有往，溝通就會止於我地互相嘅交換，而唔會互相影響到對方嘅人生。<br />\n<br />\n由於上個Post 反應好熱烈，每日都幫緊好多巴絲，亦聽大家講心事。<br />\n會占得詳細，比你抽牌同詳細解牌，唔會hea覆，如果是但玩下就留返個位比有需要嘅人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身已有好多人排緊隊，所以我會排住隊咁占，有問必應，唔會唔理你，放心。"},{"pid":"bb2c1d20af4c1f3351f6c4430a022a376956d791","tid":2023474,"uid":28251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:44:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1cc6d71cd0122158cf4043b753ccdc93831fd93","tid":2023474,"uid":28251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:44:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edfe8ef119110e320301364b4bae1feffb157a75","tid":2023474,"uid":28251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0132b1af5aa38ebab06a40952a160e1441e9c8f7","tid":2023474,"uid":28251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:45:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ec3f9df8e2f0030ddd714f460c782792195130","tid":2023474,"uid":28251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446189b22ee0b06c438a8647f0090bb3eb54ad44","tid":2023474,"uid":28251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a05426542e96b6a9ae9c26e654f29b875e3faa","tid":2023474,"uid":28251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:47:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3408ea9f9ede1033f30a331d4c15d668edd93c96","tid":2023474,"uid":28251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6245da93ee8d9848cc9f6e69258db274dbe1710","tid":2023474,"uid":28251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:47:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c8b24b562e90d54b81f87aaaa58e150bd3a0bb","tid":2023474,"uid":28251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57649dff3810ba8fb795905206ba25e39b0ea8e","tid":2023474,"uid":28251,"like":0,"dis